column5: Hey everyone We had a great day at Rice lake,  walleye cooperated from the first light, and I was happy to see my buddy getting his first Rice lake walleyes. Wind was there from early morning,  but it only did good for the eyes as they love a little chop. By 11 am we had the limit. Cheers! Gino
Good shootin. In the weeds still?
Gino--great pics, nice boat, wally's for dinner, great day !
Thanks! Was an awesome day, for sure.
Hey Cap, weeds are low this year, water is high but we found them all along the weeds. Trolled and ripped bucktail jigs. Both worked. Cheers!
Hey bud. Nice going, and nice canoe!
Nice outing! Where did you launch?
